data.description: Nice price improvement on this beautiful transitional Ranch! It is move-in ready and has everything you have been wishing for! As you enter, you will find a wonderful, open floor plan featuring formal Dining and Living Rooms with 9 ft ceilings, gleaming hardwoods, gas fireplace, surround sound and new ceiling fan. Kitchen has new granite countertops and tile backsplash, hardwoods, and stainless appliances. Enjoy eating at your sunny breakfast nook that overlooks a picturesque, fenced in backyard filled with wonderful blooming plantings, a deck and patio. The private and spacious Primary bedroom has a bay window, new ceiling fan and walk in closet. Primary bath features a double vanity upgraded with new granite countertops and tiled accent wall as well as a tile flooring, separate shower and garden tub. Split floor plan with both secondary bedrooms and upgraded bath on the opposite side of the house from the Primary allows for everyone to have their own space and privacy.  The second floor offers a great flex space to be used as you wish. Office, TV or reading room - your choice! Incredible walk-in attic allows for great storage. Laundry room has extra cabinets with new granite countertops for even more storage. The entire yard has been beautifully landscaped and filled with perennials that you will enjoy from Spring through Fall year after year. The back features two fenced areas. No need to worry about losing power since this home has a newer whole house generator. This great community features a pool, tennis courts, walking paths, club house and gazebo. Seller has added a home warranty for you. Easy access to shopping, schools and restaurants help make this location hard to beat!
